{"id":"de62021aadbb89face513d49c696d042efec259cfd9c43ac46bf4c1c9142096d","text":"PxrColorCorrect 结合了多种经典重映射和颜色校正方法。"}
{"id":"4fee20486267f8b0a35ad254419230c5f9cd4fb7911809dd006e0d4d9ebb1e4b","text":"在此连接输入颜色 pattern。"}
{"id":"e368929abd3614e92ad17e56175b67d1f6ba94aca92ab43b7f16f31764ff7447","text":"Mask"}
{"id":"c3cc6db12dd989a2817c2806b5c6e1aced0d18b0a8c0129dff65a29e0a917bc6","text":"Input Mask"}
{"id":"f8a890af383d7a3b031995363660ac959410bb2c7f23a4ece70eafaab0de36ac","text":"用于定义经过颜色校正的区域的遮罩。"}
{"id":"e2306dc9d9504be5d69402844597148581253f5fdd55b9f481eb3e373832f0d2","text":"Invert Mask"}
{"id":"ce5039bc6f8ef33334ecef675bdb2dfa8c87b9e372761104a32c72238b4acf86","text":"反转遮罩的影响。"}
{"id":"e3ccc4efba4770c7e0f4da079f035948d886ed7ef08db303c07238a3e44bdbaf","text":"Mix Mask"}
{"id":"ee6cfb23a65ea3810217bda90b013cb26c870677d482023ac4263552d5e3d31e","text":"Blend"}
{"id":"f96a63dac6081c7b0fa91e799eace96ccc93d650555ae949c171bc291217678b","text":"进遮罩中。设置为 0.0 时，完全不会进行颜色校正。"}
{"id":"cf14b48676a4f56a1248ba04e73c581255ba1ee9b49c491785fb6159fa24def6","text":"Input Range"}
{"id":"0ea3fb79b4e60d79419689efc3cf409c1dd4977a16280e0d415e56414c05d93c","text":"Input Min"}
{"id":"a29da49526cbdb5f2c7913a10c6071877998c2c4ca427f25e0785812e693ead2","text":"会将 0.0 值重映射为你选择的值。设置为 0.0 时，不会发生变化。这等同于 Photoshop 的 Levels 对话框中的黑场点。"}
{"id":"5f2baf150943ca0c79809807ce8ee5025e3e52defd023ce995d279cba8297855","text":"Input Max"}
{"id":"bf382a6f5ea66a917a0053d9e2f748ed1832dcc19b96f5e8e2fade0bf5c15f84","text":"会将 1.0 值重映射为你选择的值。设置为 1.0 时，不会发生变化。"}
{"id":"c4e5fedaa99fc544be5c72eb62e337e9682348aada0b8913ba713b2430f7d75d","text":"Color Correct"}
{"id":"7ba08588bf28e9867ed900c5b4c527cc7b5a087bcc6685c2cc13f61323b19fbc","text":"应用逐通道 gamma 校正。低于 0.0 的值会被忽略，1.0 为中性。"}
{"id":"08795ba031bcd121e4e1ce47c1c2828a796ffbf6bb4e93daeee3937017bc7a04","text":"Contrast"}
{"id":"256d9992e05a2e3e658511ffb9a4bda1321b868d5656d7199a04868183ebbded","text":"应用逐通道 Contrast。有效范围为 -1 到 +1，0.0 为中性。"}
{"id":"5fd4cd41edaf12bf98cc94067eeca75384948a218fe08dec1adc1c844965d06d","text":"Contrast Pivot"}
{"id":"037bb69abc7a64c051458f272ff25970135af07640280c59f5838a47b51559ca","text":"指定对比度曲线的逐通道枢轴。默认居中于 0.5，以模拟经典 Photoshop 风格操作。"}
{"id":"7c2a1dce40c142b90d4e6ecd9d3a15132ef560ad4604ea109aa8c3a52d922ddd","text":"RGB Gain"}
{"id":"c36d819e7bc6d2b7da51394411c733db89c395987885ca6770167a3b9bc45c3c","text":"使用"}
{"id":"faa520e3b716e67c4b0daf8588058135e276673710e05e2ef35ba87f51ae9c74","text":"为输入着色。此颜色会直接乘以输入颜色。1.0 为中性。"}
{"id":"c1242f7f888cd4e109415ca236678a95c3f8626ff07db6b27c388fbc0c77deb2","text":"HSV"}
{"id":"5e1958d2aa251f6bf855a14d45a8956596a35b49f82e09cdaf3da57e345de858","text":"应用 Hue、Saturation、Value 颜色校正。Hue 是偏移量，Saturation 和 Value 是乘数。"}
{"id":"cc5454a4b7ce211370dcd2aa0ae58d6b564eee7940b42de516d05f5b269c414b","text":"Exposure"}
{"id":"34413a746baf16295c61ec1a9aa0717cad5dd4590de8ea07368c0ab7531c85ee","text":"按给定的档数调整输入颜色的曝光。每个正档会使输入强度加倍；每个负档会使输入强度减半。通常更适合使用"}
{"id":"44affae8f5b03cd120c46f726ce919cf4040177ed18d83f47dc715fe9f15a383","text":"而不是直接乘法（例如"}
{"id":"8e8d747deb8a3d93c19afce24bfbf63da694d49240e9d2cfe25f45825430d15d","text":"），因为它在感知上线性。"}
{"id":"bb7641d053a141b28aa7317a210adf1de164bb1d0a4dacb3375e8716c0f2d40d","text":"Output Range"}
{"id":"f70659fa923402c03ef0039dbda1cafa56da38aa2d642e118308aef63181fad9","text":"Output Min"}
{"id":"7698c216e79a5b14e6095f643b28521741c52ce25bb3532d1eb580b762d50d8b","text":"会将最终颜色的 0.0 值重映射为你选择的值。"}
{"id":"1f92418cc0515aa193b718f8abb5d7b42f60ba99e22fa9a6fb96c42ac3271c9c","text":"Output Max"}
{"id":"af773f5b757c8b17a4067c76d4a597921faba6348935df18688e8f6e74b7770a","text":"会将最终颜色的 1.0 值重映射为你选择的值。"}
{"id":"79dc22e6ed3847c8ad58d2465a5b2897aa5d9033fdf3f4b131d51621133273f7","text":"Clamp Output"}
{"id":"ca0b30f713692693ae1f58b7c92f849e3971b27d84e9aa0940b29bbe65284729","text":"最终颜色可以选择进行钳制，以确保它位于用户定义范围内。"}
{"id":"09ef84bf4efcc02fe93fca7f96e1a716ab65c9672f2571764245caa9e255052f","text":"由加热到给定温度的黑体发出的颜色。"}
{"id": "e8756d05615a8b9aac2d138a9ae82553f3231ff237868a66679a30001b4f326b", "item_id": "20672d8c0f:1", "text": "Input Parameters（输入参数）"}
{"id": "35aea6f833e7d09d9722a54bdee4bc25b02fd25547d6613ee8d9457096af94fb", "item_id": "20672d8c0f:2", "text": "Input Color"}
{"id": "a8ab3d5805c9214bc66b794f599cbccd5a5958dc5a6a322ee81e3a68344c6db7", "item_id": "20672d8c0f:20", "text": "Gamma"}
{"id": "8b76e2df9050f924b018cff8809cbc580f39a71664984ae54adf99defe9eaa2e", "item_id": "20672d8c0f:48", "text": "Output Parameters"}
{"id": "d76cd2ea3537dbac1a9b90ba977fe5ad654d6f7f3c36b060963224d8b5611f99", "item_id": "20672d8c0f:49", "text": "resultRGB"}
{"id": "c9223602a8320733dcf0de118c9880f9df06acdfdb068bb26ba166fc96c52d6c", "item_id": "20672d8c0f:51", "text": "resultR"}
{"id": "c1ce276296aa97e85eded6362e0ad2b80973bc92228513facedd911006df8937", "item_id": "20672d8c0f:52", "text": "来自 resultRGB 输出的 R 通道。"}
{"id": "2e12f103dc4a4b216b21cc6f017371b08507fc67f2a1ad9f133aa333afe0fc11", "item_id": "20672d8c0f:53", "text": "resultG"}
{"id": "009cc7a7eb8d7664fe8e8a024e817626113dd5198fc3a164f5ec297f2fa68da3", "item_id": "20672d8c0f:54", "text": "来自 resultRGB 输出的 G 通道。"}
{"id": "c3719f180d82ecafb70ce347c3499e7668a3d9262533cadae303c770922865ff", "item_id": "20672d8c0f:55", "text": "resultB"}
{"id": "d1e2217f59ea1bd29de7ec3ac2c05c763eca2c3bf612f3e04ff7cfd536f9f8e0", "item_id": "20672d8c0f:56", "text": "来自 resultRGB 输出的 B 通道。"}
